features: MADE WITH REAL FRUIT PIECES: Nutrigood FruitSnax PumpkinBerry + Oats are formulated with real pumpkin and blueberries that you can see!
GREAT TASTE HORSES LOVE: FruitSnax outperforms the leading premium horse treat in consumption and sniff tests. Horses love these!
SMELL THE DIFFERENCE: So tasty, you can smell it! FruitSnax smell so amazing, you might even be tempted to try one yourself.
DELICIOUSLY HEALTHY HORSE TREATS: Made with superfoods, our FruitSnax horse treats are both healthy AND delicious. No compromises here.
NO ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS OR DYES: Feel good about pampering your horse! FruitSnax are made without any artificial flavors or dyes, so you can treat your horse without all the bad stuff.
description: Super Foods, Super Taste, Super Aroma! Nutrigood FruitSnax are delicious and flavorful treats that horses love. From the moment you open the bag, you'll be hit with an irresistible aroma that is so great, you might even be tempted to try one yourself! Each treat has pieces of real fruit that you can see, including strawberries, blueberries, cranberries and more. And with natural flavors such as pumpkin and peppermint, your horse is guaranteed to love these. FruitSnax were tested against the leading horse treats and outperformed them in consumption and sniff tests. It's proven that these are amazing! As if you needed another reason to love these, FruitSnax are packed with superfoods and include no artificial flavors or dyes, so you can feel good about pampering your horse. Choose from two irresistible flavors: PumpkinBerry + Oats and BerryMint + Oats.
